c + o = u
n + o = t
L + i = n  // 14



Gen 1 - 40 Elements -> 40 Total Elements
Gen 2 - 145 Elements -> 185 Total Elements
Gen 3 - 511 Elements -> 696 Total Elements
Gen 4 - 1582 Elements -> 2278 Total Elements
Gen 5 - 4704 Elements -> 6982 Total Elements
